Description: Daily cognitive supplement tool with smart content generation
 Awake is a desktop application that provides 10 curated items daily including
 thinking insights, good habits, knowledge points, and trend observations.
 .
 Features:
  - Smart content generation with scoring algorithm
  - User preference learning system
  - Automatic daily refresh
  - Qt5 GUI with system tray support
  - RSS subscription support
  - Cross-platform notification sounds
  - SQLite database persistence
